{"tid":1938014,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣唔鍾意化妝","createTime":"2020-03-22T09:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T22:26:48.000Z","uid":66104,"like":13,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"29f74d65c7cbe07c1f0fa67e9f6eafbb7c9b0dcf","tid":1938014,"uid":66104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"25 歲 <br />\n身邊個個都化妝 <br />\n自問皮膚無乜暗瘡 但敏感肌<br />\n成世化妝 包埋重要場合10次都有找<br />\n唔化妝係因為唔想皮膚再差落去<br />\n但就成日俾身邊朋友叫化妝<br />\n搞到我唔化好似有錯咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0761769a634cf8e33316c619d46075e49cec2624","tid":1938014,"uid":66174,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"搵啲敏感肌都可以上嘅粉底，薄薄一層，加少少胭脂算<br />\n<br />\n除非你天生麗質，如果唔係，素顏蝕底啲"},{"pid":"1db03e8d6fa0d57dff001773f996fb5f05587ae0","tid":1938014,"uid":215773,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:26:20.000Z","msg":"中女年紀冇化過妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得化左妝戴眼鏡好奇怪"},{"pid":"84aa194ac490a36f3edc16bfb0fe5ee7c8017b43","tid":1938014,"uid":36859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"化妝你唔化咁厚 揀啱底妝產品 落妝乾淨就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ab6b77e439df9eaa3d19824835b1ab4729e54b","tid":1938014,"uid":54177,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"但化左之後，<br />\n不論親戚， 朋友， 上司， 同事，甚至陌生人，<br />\n態度都好左好多，有咩都第一時間揾你，<br />\n 仲多左唔少著數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf362b01fae7534ff0503b2cdf0ecb38ca74d1f","tid":1938014,"uid":124439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"唔識化唔好化,我見D人成面粉係塊面度真係好肉酸"},{"pid":"886441a5daf6298ded00931b879022fc7738e9d5","tid":1938014,"uid":106132,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"ci